data.description: Incredible & rare opportunity! Imagine owning 2 homes for the price of one! Main home is a spacious 1088+/- SF w/ 2BD, 1.75BA. DADU is currently being fully renovated by licensed contractor & roughly 50% done. DADU is a 1bd/1ba, 432SF w/ living room that could be used as a 2nd bedroom, kitchen/dining area & its own laundry. Perfect space for guests, in-laws/parents to live nearby, or rent it out & have extra income to help pay your mortgage! Enjoy a cup of coffee w/ views of the sun rise, Mt Baker & bay from the comfort of your deck. The skies the limit w/ this property. Located on a large corner lot close to shopping, dining & easy access to Hwy 20. Don't let this gem slip away! Assumable VA loan w/ 2.75% interest rate potential!
